<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It would be helpful to have default page range be available as a static property on Zend_Paginator.  There is already a static property for default item count per page.  At the moment, to maintain consistent pagination controls, the page range must be set on each individual instance of Zend_Pagintator.</p>

<p>Patch against 1.10.6 to follow.</p>

